      "title": "The Return Is The Training",
      "image": "assets/images/background/temple.webp",
      "body": [
        {
          "text": "Every return to the breath is a small act of non-abandonment.",
          "emphasis": true
        },
        {
          "text": "The point is not to hold attention perfectly, but to learn the texture of beginning again."
        }
      ],
